<body>
    <div style="background-color: #0090e4;", class="container col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-5 col-lg-5 col-xl-5 text-white">
        <br>
        <h2>Crear Usuario</h2>
        <%= form_with model: @user do |form| %>
            <% @user.errors.full_messages.each do |error| %>
                <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
                    <%= error%> <%= alert %>
                </div>
            <% end %>

            <div class="form-group">    
                <%= form.label :nro_document,  style: "display: block" %>
                <%= form.text_field :nro_document,  class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">    
                <%= form.label :name,  style: "display: block" %>
                <%= form.text_field :name,  class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">    
                <%= form.label :username,  style: "display: block" %>
                 <%= form.text_field :username,  class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">    
                <%= form.label :email,  style: "display: block" %>
                 <%= form.email_field :email,  class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">    
                <%= form.label :password,  style: "display: block" %>
                <%= form.password_field :password,  class: "form-control", required: true %>
            </div>
            <br>
            <p>Al hacer uso de esta aplicación web estás aceptando las políticas de privacidad y tratamiento de datos personales; la cual puedes consultar en: <a href="http://localhost:3000/users/politicas/1" class="link-light">Política de privacidad aquí</a></br>
            ¿Si estás de acuerdo selecciona la siguiente casilla? <input id="myCheckbox" type="checkbox" />
            <script> 
                const checkbox = document.getElementById('myCheckbox')

                checkbox.addEventListener('change', (event) => {
                if (event.currentTarget.checked) {
                   $('#submitButton').attr('disabled', false);
                } else {
                    $('#submitButton').attr('disabled', true);
                }
                })
            </script>
            </p>

            <%= form.hidden_field :document_id, :value => 1, class: "form-control" %>
            <%= form.hidden_field :authorization_date, :value => Time.now, class: "form-control" %>
            <%= form.hidden_field :authorization_police, :value => 1, class: "form-control" %>
            <div>
            <%= form.submit value= t('common.submitlog'), id: "submitButton", disabled: true  %>     
            <br>
        <% end %>
    </div> 
</body>
<div></br></div>
